<td tEditID="c1r2" style=" background-color:#FFFFFF; color:#000000; bEditID:r3st1; bLabel:main; font-size:12pt; font-family:arial;" aEditID="c1r2" locked="0" >
<![CDATA[<span id="docs-internal-guid-678969b4-a189-a0b9-0355-a0ba66473fe3"><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><p style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Dear&nbsp;<span style="white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">{!Contact.FirstName},</span></p><p style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></p><p style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">I am pleased that you have conditionally accepted a position to serve as a Support Worker this&nbsp;<b>SUMMER</b>. As part of this conditional hire we need to match you with a young person. In order to do this I need to send anonymised sensitive information about the young person to you and therefore will need you to sign a confidentiality agreement since you are not yet contractually employed by The Challenge.</p><p style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></p><p style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"></p><p style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Please do not hesitate to call if there is anything you would like to clarify. I would be grateful if you would print, read and return a signed copy of the <a href="https://staffing.the-challenge.org/assets/INCLUSION_DISCLOSURE_AGREEMENT_2016.docx">attached agreement</a> no later than <b>1 week</b> after receiving this email.&nbsp;A scanned copy with signature returned by email fulfils the requirements.</p><p style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></p><p style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Return the scanned copy to&nbsp;<a href="mailto:inclusionroles@the-challenge.org" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(17, 85, 204);">inclusionroles@the-challenge.<wbr>org</a>&nbsp;which will be added to your profile and allow me to start the matching process.</p><p style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></p><p style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">I will be in contact with you in the coming weeks when the matching process with young people is underway.</p><p style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></p><p style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"></p><p style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Yours sincerely,</p><p style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></p><p style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span id="docs-internal-guid-fe7c54bc-a494-5a0a-46f8-53b3d3cf18ad"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">{!Job_placement__c.Staffing_Associate__c}</span></span></p></font></span>]]></td>
